videos.headline: Northwestern defender makes incredible one-handed INT
videos.description: Northwestern's Montre Hartage tracks back on the football and ends up pulling off an unbelievable one-handed interception against Indiana.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Northwestern defender makes incredible one-handed INT) 2016/10/22 ESHEET
